         <div xml:lang="en" type="translation">
            <ab>"Papontos, alias Patas, overseer of the lower estate and upper estate, to the most honorable Matreas, greetings.;If it should seem best to you, lord, send to Epimas and Heras for trasnporting chaff for firing the pots in the pottery establishment of the lower for the production of the twentieth year (x drachmas), for which I shall furnish an accounting . . . "</ab>
